'''Chris David''' (born 14 June 1953) is an English [[audio engineering|sound engineer]]. He was nominated for an [[Academy Awards|Academy Award]] in the category [[Academy Award for Best Sound Mixing|Best Sound]] for the film ''[[Legends of the Fall]]''.<ref name="Oscars1995">{{Cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1995 |title=The 67th Academy Awards (1995) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=23 October 2011|work=oscars.org}}</ref> He has worked on 170-plus films since 1982.

==Selected filmography==
* ''[[Legends of the Fall]]'' (1994)

