Bottle/Vase: Measuring 6-3/4" high and 4-1/4" in dameter. Whitish glaze with underglaze cobalt blue decoration of a floral branch spread over most of the bottle at the lower part of the flaring neck is very simple and long. Yi dynasty. 17th century.
