'''Douglas Ganton''' is an American [[audio engineering|sound engineer]]. He was nominated for an [[Academy Awards|Academy Award]] in the category [[Academy Award for Best Sound Mixing|Best Sound]]. for the film ''[[Legends of the Fall]]''.<ref name="Oscars1995">{{Cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1995 |title=The 67th Academy Awards (1995) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=October 23, 2011|work=oscars.org}}</ref> He worked on 75 films from 1975 to 2009.

==Selected filmography==
* ''[[Legends of the Fall]]'' (1994)

